  <brief_title>Effect of High Dose Insulin on Infectious Complications Following Major Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Hyperinsulinemic Normoglycemic Clamp (HINC) on Infectious Complications Following Major Abdominal Surgery. A Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
